    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款单人FPS游戏，在游戏中你可以体验第一人称射击的乐趣，步兵模式下可选择拥有7把突击步枪和机枪，2种手枪和一个手雷。一张紧凑的步战地图。在载具模式下，可以自由切换第一人称和第三人称，可以驾驶包括：M1A2，M2A3，M1128，T90，2S23，BMP-2这些坦克和步战车，坦克和步兵战车AI拥有较高的智商，它们会选择对威胁大的目标开火，即使你在远处向它们射击，它们仍然能找到你并向你还击！载具战中拥有一张超大的沙漠地图，去占领多个据点。另外游戏的武器可以自由搭配配件，每把主武器可以使用6种不同的瞄准镜以及装配或卸下消音器和红外线。此外，武器的皮肤外观可以根据你的喜好去更改，在游戏中获取你的磁盘上的任意一张png格式的图片来定制属于你自己的枪皮肤！最后游戏还提供人数、特效以及时间分数等关卡设置，自由搭配它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可驾驶的载具：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302670/extras/73a03cbde908963fd67c627320c25cf3.avif?t=1755699153\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302670/extras_big/73a03cbde908963fd67c627320c25cf3.avif?t=1755699153 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302670/extras/ebadcfb7a5a54335d34f5bb597633f59.avif?t=1755699153\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302670/extras_big/ebadcfb7a5a54335d34f5bb597633f59.avif?t=1755699153 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302670/extras/49fa88bc2908c47b66fa7d536d37deef.avif?t=1755699153\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302670/extras_big/49fa88bc2908c47b66fa7d536d37deef.avif?t=1755699153 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302670/extras/3ec2fa62fd3dac5cafc0c435f305894a.avif?t=1755699153\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302670/extras_big/3ec2fa62fd3dac5cafc0c435f305894a.avif?t=1755699153 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_i